<pc>”</pc>
<measure quantity="2" unit="people">
<num value="2">二</num>人</measure>
<num value="1">一</num>見奇之<pc>，</pc>待遇甚厚<pc>。</pc>仲淹以<pc>《</pc>
<title>左氏春秋</title>
